                "content": "Requesting source details:\n- Which prime price index underpins the -8% QoQ figure (provider/methodology)?\n- Does the reported -22% DLD change refer to transaction count or transaction value, and what is the comparison base (QoQ vs. MoM)?\nWe will share the official DLD April monthly statistics once they are released.",
